cs.FL, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.PL, cs.CC 

The paper deals with the determinization of B\"uchi automata, which is a topic in formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL). It also involves the construction of automata based on tree structures (cs.DS) and parity automata (cs.PL). The paper also discusses heuristics for improving the determinization process (cs.CC). Finally, the paper involves mathematical proofs and logic (cs.LO) in the development of the new meta-construction.
